('### 11.3. Obtener el número de Seguridad Social  
**Posibles dificultades:**
En la práctica, para autentificarte telemáticamente necesitas la tarjeta vigente, lo que a veces genera "un laberinto" hasta que te dejan hacerlo con la cara del pasaporte. El movimiento está trabajando para facilitar estos mecanismos y preparar instrucciones claras (*"vale, tienes que decir tal, tal, tal, y a la tercera ya la tienes"*).', '[-0.012313772,-0.0037054769,0.0025288665,-0.05149983,-0.0063141133,0.017041847,0.011236098,0.020370282,-0.00069204246,-0.0013316707,-0.01573693,0.031829145,0.021462776,0.038422488,0.13225216,0.010052552,0.004473437,0.018496463,-0.012226859,-0.024437603,0.03540146,-0.0041478537,-0.037879407,-0.009256695,-0.00454665,0.0020171155,0.021467945,0.0093164,0.033249818,-0.024428677,0.00929884,0.014401413,0.006645995,0.04477997,-0.031862486,0.02288893,0.009611458,-0.014211687,-0.012342393,0.010537433,0.016394721,0.0020945338,0.0026466062,-0.011784272,0.0129618365,-0.004925369,-0.0011782232,-0.015431453,0.0022027963,0.007104914,-0.00019891016,0.023530796,-0.038376193,-0.16794027,0.012078947,-0.023110224,0.004066588,0.010396466,-0.008109741,-0.023451308,-0.02858073,0.028598318,-0.006334389,-0.0065682465,0.011115478,0.00029399607,0.033814818,0.031574227,-0.0022855015,-0.019620365,-0.0044516306,-0.007048933,-0.008877057,-0.02965165,0.011452985,-0.011271161,-0.010243701,0.009049724,0.00048812234,-0.0025839147,-0.029557588,-0.0019919693,0.0016362205,-0.007950103,0.02454598,-0.020642236,0.025525158,0.010984198,-0.008152569,0.015791455,0.0055473964,0.024874512,0.0012265409,-0.022274962,0.021666978,-0.006880476,-0.014133082,0.007550317,0.0025803072,-0.0060400954,-0.015543976,-0.0140174925,-0.00063215365,0.00517929,0.016831523,-0.044916913,-0.019577438,0.0038782572,0.00023424249,3.590366e-05,-0.009368684,0.009427793,0.0015621617,0.012750419,0.018531205,-0.16961123,-0.009644578,0.01222713,-0.011131489,-0.0053154104,0.020202838,0.012472752,0.0040669264,0.0070608323,-0.0049041584,4.483526e-05,0.02320005,-0.031101229,0.00044934943,0.00040384269,0.014875