('### 12.9. Persona en trámite activo de arraigo  
**Perfil:** Persona con arraigo en curso (sociolaboral, socioformativo o social), sin poder trabajar ni salir del país mientras espera resolución.  
**Pregunta:** "¿Puedo acogerme a la regularización extraordinaria si ya tengo un arraigo en trámite?"  
**Respuesta:** **SÍ**, en principio.  
**Explicación:** Puedes acogerte a la regularización extraordinaria aunque tengas un arraigo en curso. El trámite de arraigo quedará en pausa — no se pierde. Las solicitudes de arraigo en trámite se resolverán favorablemente si se cumplen los requisitos de la regularización extraordinaria, sin necesidad de volver a presentar documentación. No renuncies al arraigo.', '[0.007376821,0.029852884,0.01971844,-0.069440715,0.0053004203,0.013555628,0.012527798,0.016847694,0.0030010254,-0.014463257,0.00028776587,-0.00026466988,0.0036424801,0.017540019,0.122915454,-0.009740228,0.00859209,0.024412265,-0.009932097,-0.011452599,0.02873583,-0.0029296572,-0.03689167,0.010088369,-0.021225682,0.023545666,0.03050078,0.0076111224,0.040488828,-0.034667242,-0.019105572,0.012982081,0.0014748233,0.03261218,-0.015496623,0.02773111,-0.004214469,-0.0012322287,-0.013351007,0.0017258128,0.022548424,0.0029549587,-0.011928072,0.013607944,0.037488032,-0.0013900772,-0.024411144,-0.027209152,-0.018694537,0.0040274956,0.0008382351,0.007701418,-0.026854008,-0.16826285,-0.0009592408,-0.007860718,-0.004426451,-0.0020195972,0.008230272,-0.007039657,-0.027092049,0.03259431,-0.012378538,-0.0050653196,0.008952546,0.0075202314,0.00199966,0.02878645,0.015265194,-0.020081293,0.011685143,-0.010123906,0.007833419,-0.0016058312,0.012769358,-0.03060344,-0.002664943,0.016079303,-0.017770749,0.006293135,0.021555435,0.013949674,0.008304604,-0.016697329,0.015979074,0.0039216042,0.02369931,0.014615716,-0.028029492,-0.0021227582,0.016211635,0.018950423,0.005661727,-0.032275908,0.00026264574,-0.0060476,0.0016122187,0.012823465,-0.007203911,-0.02633795,-0.029248357,-0.01515008,-0.0019197827,0.012688235,0.017868074,-0.029075913,0.0036876136,0.006844946,-0.0011721815,-0.0039718784,0.014661777,-0.024648782,0.008910038,0.013606001,0.008399263,-0.16245995,0.024564248,-0.011278321,-0.004298288,-0.008735891,0.0012893694,0.013461045,0.011058851,0.0038978746,0.01024225,-0.014899442,-0.0067373244,-0.025239354,-0.015855294,0.0030853