('### 12.15. Multa por estancia irregular  
**Perfil:** Persona en proceso de regularización a quien se le ha aplicado una multa por estancia irregular.  
**Pregunta:** "Esta mañana me aplicaron una multa por estancia irregular. ¿Afectará eso a mi proceso de regularización extraordinaria?"  
**Respuesta:** **NO debería afectar.**  
**Explicación:** El texto previsto indica que los procedimientos de expulsión o devolución iniciados por estancia irregular quedarán **archivados automáticamente** una vez que se conceda la autorización de residencia. La multa no bloquea la solicitud ni la resolución.', '[0.0014152462,0.03008556,0.027939158,-0.06622925,0.025719663,0.019281227,0.017863454,0.009704032,0.015355775,-0.006992525,0.0012836355,0.010500669,0.0067060064,0.006868817,0.11461846,0.0068830224,0.009455208,0.016722323,0.0004930818,-0.009364702,0.024977358,0.008753387,-0.020764755,-0.008108199,-0.036001693,0.00832472,0.03878198,0.020556182,0.049289368,-0.017646678,-0.020619156,0.026404167,0.0041856365,0.02833738,-0.022710634,0.03187894,-0.0013545651,0.0058041876,-0.0012479755,-0.003711192,0.004157913,-0.0072746347,-0.008041217,0.01456655,0.02756377,-0.015542197,-0.01343647,-0.03390612,-0.02531232,0.010925424,-0.004376429,-0.0044079972,-0.040092666,-0.16456364,0.020003082,-0.006128565,-0.004779336,-0.0063459906,0.010121563,-0.013302586,-0.03310555,0.030165847,-0.015339386,-0.010266834,0.0021906297,0.007811769,-0.0043000174,0.028165592,0.0007220871,-0.017417315,0.013744027,-0.013531793,-0.00041411305,-0.0033398774,0.016446244,-0.017323608,0.018499643,0.020149091,-0.018240647,0.0075028786,0.0131876515,0.02323056,0.0063206633,-0.021819942,0.0096588405,0.0013259089,0.01214779,0.0040060394,-0.023384906,0.017310144,0.00626731,0.008913043,0.0003516882,-0.025894754,-0.016623873,0.007709379,0.0031047296,0.023568232,-0.001875965,-0.04470959,-0.017656477,-0.015640168,0.0064094085,0.022586808,0.028264685,-0.010950532,0.0048053,0.017728867,-0.00604018,-0.020902246,0.009165849,-0.015590239,0.0039183227,0.019537231,0.0036913462,-0.17150182,0.0404431,-0.0078021763,-0.0068772538,-0.020686662,0.0039876318,0.030604552,0.008946965,0.01563795,-0.009149846,-0.031118857,0.0017468391,-0.01004487,2.8104929e-05,-0.004209717,0.0102088675,-0.0024268697,0.009174933,-0.0020495516,-0.020701563,0.019182317,-0.0144005185,-0.0052064